Penoles to pay dividend of 1 . 36 pesos . Industrias Penoles , the world ' s largest refined silver producer , said on Thursday it will pay a cash dividend of 1 . 36 pesos per share . The company said in a statement to the Mexican Stock Exchange that it had not yet set a date for paying the dividend . It said it had 404 , 494 , 747 shares outstanding . The firm said also that its recent shareholders ' meeting approved creating reserves of 200 million pesos to buy back company shares . ( ( - - Mexico City newsroom + 525 728 - 9565 ) ) 
